<style>
  .about-wrap { max-width: 860px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 24px; }
  .about-hero-title { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 48px; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .about-hero-text { font-size: 18px; color: var(--muted); max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; line-height: 1.7; }
  .about-grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 40px; margin-bottom: 60px; }
  .about-story-title { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 28px; color: var(--dark); margin-bottom: 16px; }
  .about-mission-title { font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: 32px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .about-wrap { padding: 28px 16px; }
    .about-hero-title { font-size: 30px; }
    .about-hero-text { font-size: 15px; }
    .about-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 32px; }
    .about-story-title { font-size: 22px; }
    .about-mission { padding: 28px 20px !important; border-radius: 16px !important; }
    .about-mission-title { font-size: 24px; }
    .about-mission p { font-size: 14px !important; }
    .about-mission a { padding: 12px 24px !important; font-size: 14px !important; }
  }
</style>

<div class="about-wrap">

  <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;color:var(--green);font-size:14px;text-decoration:none;margin-bottom:32px;">← Back to Home</a>

  <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px;">
    <div style="font-size:48px;margin-bottom:16px;">🐾</div>
    <h1 class="about-hero-title">About Pawfield</h1>
    <p class="about-hero-text">We believe every pet deserves the best — and every pet parent deserves to find it easily.</p>
  </div>

  <div class="about-grid">
    <div>
      <h2 class="about-story-title">Our Story</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:16px;">Pawfield was born from a simple frustration — finding high-quality pet products that actually work shouldn't be so hard. We spent months researching, testing, and handpicking products from trusted suppliers worldwide so you don't have to.</p>
      <p style="color:var(--muted);line-height:1.8;">From smart feeders to calming beds, every product in our catalog is selected based on quality, durability, and real pet-parent reviews.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:var(--cream);border-radius:20px;padding:32px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;">
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;">🌍</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:4px;">Worldwide Sourcing</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);">Hand-selected from trusted global suppliers</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;">🚚</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:4px;">Fast US Delivery</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);">Most orders arrive within 6–12 business days</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;">🔄</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:4px;">30-Day Returns</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);">Not happy? Full refund, no questions asked</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;">
        <div style="font-size:32px;">💬</div>
        <div>
          <div style="font-weight:600;color:var(--dark);margin-bottom:4px;">Real Support</div>
          <div style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);">We respond to every message within 24 hours</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="about-mission" style="background:var(--green);border-radius:24px;padding:48px;text-align:center;color:white;">
    <h2 class="about-mission-title">Our Mission</h2>
    <p style="font-size:16px;opacity:0.9;max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 28px;line-height:1.7;">To make premium pet care accessible to every pet parent — because your furry family members deserve nothing less than the best.</p>
    <a href="/collections/all" style="display:inline-block;background:white;color:var(--green);padding:14px 32px;border-radius:50px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;font-size:15px;">Shop Our Collection →</a>
  </div>

</div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About Us",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
